    {"slug": "1672760368-i-am-the-fated-villain", "title": "I Am the Fated Villain", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/fatedvillain-2.jpg", "rating": 9.9, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['Immediately after Gu Changge realized he had transgressed into a fantasy world, the world\u2019s protagonist, and fortune\u2019s chosen, vowed to take revenge on him. Envied by all, he not only has the female lead head over heels for him but he\u2019s also treated as a distinguished guest wherever he goes. Fortunately, Gu Changge\u2019s prestige and power are superior to everyone else\u2019s, so shouldn\u2019t it be easy to trample on a mere fortune\u2019s chosen?', '\\xa0', 'Hold on\u2026 There\u2019s a system dedicated to milking and harvesting from the protagonist? Gu Changge smirked. \u201cSeems like even fate wants me to fulfill my destiny as the Villain of this world!\u201d']", "released": "Sen", "artist": "-", "category": "Manhua", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Cultivation", "Fantasy", "Isekai", "Martial Arts", "System", "Villain"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-heavenly-swords-grand-saga", "title": "Heavenly Sword\u2019s Grand Saga", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/grandSagaCover02.png", "rating": 9.8, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['[From the author of ', ']', 'There are people in the world that thinks they are the \u2018chosen\u2019 of the heavens. It\u2019s been decades since chaos and strife among heroes ensued because of those people. A certain disciple who has six masters has been entrusted with the fate of the central plains. \u201cIf you guys are the heavens, then I\u2019m the sword that\u2019ll pierce the heavens.\u201d That was what he\u2019d resolved to do\u2026 No one mentioned he was a fatty, though! In any case, now that he\u2019s here, he\u2019ll need to save the\u2026 world\u2026 Damn it, lose some weight first.', '\\xa0']", "released": "MED", "artist": "-", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Adventure", "Comedy", "Martial Arts", "Murim"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-heavenly-martial-god", "title": "Heavenly Martial God", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/martialgod.jpg", "rating": 9.3, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['\u201cWho\u2019s this male prostitute-looking kid?\u201d I am the Matchless Ha Hoo Young, the greatest martial artist reigning over all the lands! There is no one that is my equal! I was drowning in futility and emptiness because there was no more that I could accomplish in the human realm. To reach the peak of martial arts, I must become a saint! \u201cI finally succeeded!!!\u201d \u201cStop! Your ascension is not permitted!\u201d The other saints refused my ascension due to my karma after much slaughter, and I fell, just like that.', '\\nWhen I woke up, I was 60 years in the future. I was reborn as the second lord of the Namgoong family, Namgoong Hyuk. Where has all the internal energy that I\u2019ve accumulated gone?! Moreover, I have the Nine yin energy blockage?']", "released": "MED", "artist": "-", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Adventure", "Martial Arts"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-heavenly-inquisition-sword", "title": "Heavenly Inquisition Sword", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/inquisitionSwordCover02.png", "rating": 9.5, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['\u201cHe is the master of the Nine Heavens.\u201d', 'Yeon Jeokha was the child of a second wife. Viciously bullied by his father\u2019s first wife and his siblings, he was later imprisoned in a warehouse after his father died of illness\u2026', 'It has been ten years since his escape after he had learned martial arts that were out of the world.', '\u201cI regard the Yeon Family with great bitterness.\u201d', 'The unstoppable adventure of the sole successor of the Heavenly Inquisition Sword, Yeon Jeokha, begins now!']", "released": "Kita", "artist": "Redice Studio", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Adventure", "Martial Arts", "Murim"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-genius-of-the-unique-lineage", "title": "Genius of the Unique Lineage", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/geniusLineageCover01.png", "rating": 9.5, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['I want to be someone who kills invaders', '__', 'I want to kill invaders and live a happy daily life in a special world.', '\\nCan\u2019t I just ask for that?', '\\nWhy? Why can\u2019t I do that?', '\\nPeople say chasing two different rabbits will make you miss both, but\u2026', '\\njust don\u2019t miss them.']", "released": "Kita", "artist": "JC Studio", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Adventure", "Fantasy"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-helmut-the-forsaken-child", "title": "Helmut: The Forsaken Child", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/helmutCover01.png", "rating": 9.8, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['Helmut was a child who had been abandoned in the Demonic Beast Forest at birth.', '\\nRaised by Demonic Beasts, the first human that he met was the Sword Saint Darien.', '\\nLittle did Helmut know that the chance encounter would soon shake the foundation of his fate\u2026', '\u201cGrow stronger If you want to get out of here.\u201d', 'The boy who\u2019d lived like a beast was thrown into the human world!', '\\nHe possessed overwhelming swordsmanship, outstanding looks and sharp intelligence, but there was one thing he lacked: humanity.', 'I am no longer prey. I am now a predator!']", "released": "Kita", "artist": "Khit Studio", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Adventure", "Fantasy", "Shounen"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-for-my-forsaken-beloved", "title": "For My Forsaken Beloved", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/unknown-4.png", "rating": 9.2, "status": "Dropped",
        "description": "['\u201cSave my dearest love!\u201d Hestia, who loved the incomplete romantic fantasy novel enough to isekai, was insignificant, even among the extras who got possessed.', '\\nFinally, the novel has come to its end with her watching the main characters in person! The conclusion of the novel left her thinking that she\u2019d return to her world, but that thought turned to ashes. She was shocked when she found out about the novel\u2019s behind-the-scenes ending that showed the death of her beloved, the sub male lead Caelus. Without even taking a break, she regresses\u2026! \u2018This time, I will protect my beloved!\u2019']", "released": "MED", "artist": "-", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Drama", "Fantasy", "Returner", "Romance"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-existence", "title": "Existence", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/existenceCover01.png", "rating": 9.9, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['One day, it was a herd of ants, and another day, it was a large dinosaur.', '\\nThis was the last reincarnation of a being that had experienced tens of thousands of reincarnations and lives.', 'He was born as a human with the power of every single lifeform he had ever been.', 'Why did he have such an ability?', '\\nLee Jain finally came to understand.', '\u201cI exist to eradicate mankind.\u201d']", "released": "Kita", "artist": "Mapakam X SuperComix", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Adventure", "Fantasy", "Overpowered"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-heavenly-demon-instructor", "title": "Heavenly Demon Instructor", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/heavenlydemoninstructor-1.jpg", "rating": 9.6, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['\u201cMaster, what\u2019s the next lesson?!!!\u201d', '\\xa0', 'A disaster that struck the earth, [Portal Impact], caused Park Hyunsoo, the MC, to lose his parents before his eyes.', '\\nThe only family member he has left is his younger sibling who is unconscious.', '\\nIn order to protect his younger sibling, he did his best but as a powerless support, he would always be on the other side of contempt\u2026', '\\nAnd that\u2019s when a helper, Chungyeong, appeared!', '\\nChungyeong, a murim martial master that has travelled through time to come here from the Murim to teach Hyunsoo martial arts\u2026', '\\xa0', '\u201cHey, disciple\u2026\u201d', '\\n\u201cYes, Master.\u201d', '\\xa0']", "released": "Blu", "artist": "Jodol", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "Hwabong, Kim Jaka", "genres": ["Action", "Adventure", "Dungeons", "Fantasy", "Martial Arts", "Monsters", "Murim", "Shounen", "System"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-ending-maker", "title": "Ending Maker", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ending_maker_01.jpg", "rating": 9.7, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['There are two people who were obssessed with the game, Legend of Heroes 2, and spent thousands of hours on it.', '\\nThe forever number one, Kang Jinho, and the forever number two, Hong Yoohee.', '\\nOne day, when they woke up, they had been reincarnated into their characters within the game\u2026', '\u201cHey\u2026 You too?\u201d', '\\n\u201cHey\u2026 Me too!\u201d', 'Legend of Heroes 2\u2019s ending is the end of the human world.', 'However, since there are two of them instead of just one, and not just any two, but the server\u2019s rank one and rank two, things could be different.', 'The journey of the veteran gamers to accomplish the happy ending starts now!']", "released": "Cc Sword", "artist": "-", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Comedy", "Fantasy", "Romance", "Video Game"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-i-reincarnated-as-the-crazed-heir", "title": "I Reincarnated As The Crazed Heir", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Title-Cover-kopya.png", "rating": 9.2, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['Yang Jagak, who was assassinated through poison during the political wars of the', 'Murim. While he thought he was dead, he realized he was in the body of another person.', 'He found out that he is in the Demon Cult, the art he knows is the Heavenly Demon God Arts, and the owner of the body was the crazed heir who lusted after women.', 'Why did it need to be the Demon Cult, and why did it need to be this person?', '\\xa0', '\\xa0']", "released": "Euwen", "artist": "Jeon Madu/ Redice Studio", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "Eunho", "genres": ["Action", "Martial Arts", "Reincarnation"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-murim-login", "title": "Murim Login", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/LoginMoorimCover05.png", "rating": 9.9, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['An era where hunters thrive on hunting monsters that come from Gates. Jin Tae-Kyung is a low-rank hunter who picks up a VR machine, and accidentally logs into the game, which is set in the world of Martial Arts. After many ups and downs, Tae-Kyung is able to escape this world. The strength and skills, which he received in the Murim were able to be carried over back to the real world. This allows him to continue making a living a hunter\u2026 but he decides to return back to the world of Murim, out of care for his NPC friends.', '\\xa0']", "released": "MED", "artist": "Jang Cheol-Byuk", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "Zerobic", "genres": ["Action", "Adventure", "Comedy", "Fantasy", "Martial Arts", "Seinen"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-emperors-domination", "title": "Emperor\u2019s Domination", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/f3556622c9ac203f7800dd88f8efe81126b1bbf8.jpg", "rating": 9.0, "status": "Dropped",
        "description": "['The rise of revered cultivators has been witnessed for countless years.', 'However, the eyes of the world fail to notice that, behind every cultivator, there seems to be a mysterious\u2026', 'Yin crow. After the Yin crow guided a legion of young cultivators to the peak of cultivation and established a sect, he chose to leave and abandon it.', '\\nThousands of years have passed since his departure, and circumstances have changed. The once brilliant sect was left in shambles and vulnerable to imminent danger.', 'Aware of the impending downfall, the Yin crow returned as a young boy in order to fulfill his agreement to guard and restore the sect to its former glory.']", "released": "Blu", "artist": "-", "category": "Manhua", "author": "-", "genres": []},
    {"slug": "1672760368-maxed-out-leveling", "title": "Maxed Out Leveling", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/resource-1-1-1.jpg", "rating": 9.8, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['Max-level internal arts, max-level external arts.', 'Jianghu, Murim\u2019s famous and strongest, Cha Shin Hyeon.', 'I came back to Earth after reaching the peak of martial arts, but why has everything changed so much?', 'A world where monsters are coming out of dungeons, and hunters are leveling up via their status windows.', '\u2018Start again from level one? That doesn\u2019t phase me at all, since my martial arts are already at the max level.\u2019']", "released": "asura", "artist": "-", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Fantasy", "Murim", "Overpowered", "Returner", "System"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-mookhyang-the-origin", "title": "Mookhyang The Origin", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/ponytail_boy_.png", "rating": 9.8, "status": "Completed",
        "description": "['In a world with bloody and vast battlefields where several forces fought for supremacy; a young boy only known as number 2044, was kidnapped and trained to be an assassin by the enemy since he was a child. After much intensive training and struggling through life-threatening situations, he gained the name \u201cMukhyang\u201d. But Mukhyang was never satisfied, he had an unfulfilled thirst for something, and that was the path of the sword! As Mukhyang was dissatisfied with his life as an assassin, he met his mentor \u2018Yu Baek of the Hwan Sa Sword\u2019 and his life changed forever. Will he be able to reach the pinnacle of martial arts?!', 'Fighting with geniuses as he climbs his way to the top!']", "released": "asura", "artist": "-", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Adaptation", "Martial Arts", "Shounen", "Wuxia"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-my-civil-servant-life-reborn-in-the-strange-world", "title": "My Civil Servant Life Reborn in the Strange World", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/bitchassmofo.jpg", "rating": 9.0, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['He was on his way to buy some beer to celebrate his acceptance as a civil servant when he was suddenly banged down and isekai\u2019d by truck-kun.', 'Reincarnated as Denburg Blade, the son of a legendary battle race chief, he caught demons at 8 years old and a dragon at 12 years old. Subjected to the spartan-style training of his muscular monster of a father, he lived an inhuman daily life.', '\u201cI must leave this place that is far from peaceful!\u201d', 'Safety is the best! So he chose to be a civil servant of the empire!', 'Can Denburg really become a civil servant and live the peaceful and stable life he wished for?']", "released": "MED", "artist": "Redice Studio", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "\uc77c\uacc4", "genres": ["Fantasy", "Overpowered", "Reincarnation", "Shounen"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-life-of-a-magic-academy-mage", "title": "Life of a Magic Academy Mage", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/magicAcademyMageCover02.png", "rating": 9.7, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['Life as a magic academy mage. Graduate student Lee Han was born as the youngest son in another world\u2019s famous family of mages. He swore he would never go to another place with the word \u201cacademy\u201d in it. However, the magic academy known as Einrogard completely ignored what he had promised himself. Being self-sufficient is a must; monsters may appear, and the professors are all total nutjobs! This is the beginning of a pitiful academy life that you have never seen before.', '\u201cWill I be able to\u2026 graduate safely?\u201d', '\\xa0']", "released": "Kita", "artist": "APTX", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "Writing Machine", "genres": ["Action", "Adventure", "Comedy", "Fantasy", "Magic", "School Life"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-max-level-returner", "title": "Max Level Returner", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/COVER-ENG-1.jpg", "rating": 10.0, "status": "Dropped",
        "description": "['120 million people have disappeared worldwide.', '[Final Quest Completion Reward: \u2018Return\u2019 Activated]', 'For the first time in 22 years, Yoon Sang-Hyuk cleared the world\u2019s worst survival game.', '\\nHe, the so-called strongest person among all other players, one who possess all reward items even the ones that no one else could earn, has come back.', '[Return of the Masked Monarch]', 'I alone am level 10,000, I alone have all the items, only me!']", "released": "asura", "artist": "-", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Adventure", "Fantasy", "Martial Arts"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-legend-of-mir-the-golden-armored-dragon", "title": "Legend of Mir: The Golden Armored Dragon", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/resource-1.jpg", "rating": 8.0, "status": "Dropped",
        "description": "['\u201cWhere am I?\u201d', '\\n\u201cWhat\u2026 am I?\u201d', 'In the world of a game, the guardian monster of the 7th floor of the abyss, the Golden Armored Dragon, has become self-aware!!', 'In his dragon form, he is clad in golden armour, but when he completes a certain amount of quests, the Golden Armored Dragon can then polymorph into his human form and come out to the field. He is accompanied by Dorothy, a rare character in the game, who calls him by the name \u2018Goldy\u2019; the leader of the Golden Dragon attack squad and the pillar of the Crimson Blood clan, Juk Oon Chan; and Zepeto, a girl with the nickname \u2018Dumpling Hair\u2019\u2026', 'In the Murim of the virtual reality martial arts game \u2018The Legend of New Mirr\u2019, their story begins!']", "released": "asura", "artist": "-", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Fantasy", "Martial Arts", "Shounen", "Virtual Game"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-legendary-youngest-son-of-the-marquis-house-manhwa", "title": "Legendary Youngest Son of the Marquis House", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/legendarymarquis.jpg", "rating": 9.9, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['I came here with only the goal of revenge.', 'I overthrew the Tulkan Empire, a single nation that dominated the continent.', 'I had always succeeded in gaining victory. I had accomplished all I needed to and was satisfied.', 'That\u2019s why I accepted my approaching death. I no longer had a reason to live.', 'And so my heart stopped beating.', 'I definitely felt it stop.', 'However, what in the world happened?', '\u201cIt\u2019s not black magic and it doesn\u2019t seem like an illusion either.\u201d', 'A boy with short, black hair was reflected in the mirror.', 'I looked exactly like when I was 14, which was 20 years ago. A young boy, who hasn\u2019t lost his baby fat yet, patted his cheeks and murmured, \u201cHow is this possible?\u201d.', 'I had returned.', 'To the time filled with my regrets.', '\\xa0']", "released": "MED", "artist": "-", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Fantasy", "Rebirth", "Shounen"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-legend-of-asura-the-venom-dragon", "title": "Legend of Asura \u2013 The Venom Dragon", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Illustration4.jpg", "rating": 9.4, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['The long history of the Medical Sect is followed by complete and utter annihilation.', 'In a hellhole of despair, where corpses pile up like mountains and blood flows like the sea, \u2018Asura\u2019 finally awakens.', '\u2013 I\u2019ll kill every single one of them.', '\\nIt won\u2019t be over until I\u2019ve killed them all.', 'The sole survivor of the Medical Sect\u2019s, Jin Ja Gang \u2013', 'Follow his lonesome path to vengeance!', '\\xa0']", "released": "asura", "artist": "Ant Studio", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Adaptation", "Fantasy", "Martial Arts", "Wuxia"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-kill-the-dragon", "title": "Kill The Dragon", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/coverrr.jpg", "rating": 9.5, "status": "Ongoing",
        "description": "['\\xa0', '\u201cDo everything you can to survive.\u201d Humans were told by their invaders, the \u2018Dragons\u2019, that they would be exterminated. Before the world collapsed, the person who will protect the world, a war orphan, Lee Han, awakened as a \u2018Psyker\u2019.', '\\xa0']", "released": "MED", "artist": "Redice Studio", "category": "Manhwa", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Fantasy", "Shounen", "Supernatural"]},
    {"slug": "1672760368-king-of-runes", "title": "King of Runes", "image": "https://www.asurascans.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/king-of-runes-1.jpg", "rating": 8.9, "status": "Dropped",
        "description": "['Dongze was an ordinary senior student from the Huangshi District of the Reigu Region, but with the help of a game system, he ended up becoming the chief commander of the Eastern Warzone.', 'He led humanity and drove the runestone beasts back to the wormhole they came from, allowing life on Earth to regain its usual peace.']", "released": "Blu", "artist": "-", "category": "Manhua", "author": "-", "genres": ["Action", "Adventure", "Fantasy", "Monsters"]},
